{
  "video_id": "RQTjqMHgNZU",
  "title": "讓設計永恆的秘密：George Arriola at TEDxTaipei 2014",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 5230.0,
      "end_time": 7501.0,
      "text": "Good afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7501.0,
      "end_time": 9150.0,
      "text": "Thought I'd try to be like Zuck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9150.0,
      "end_time": 13738.0,
      "text": "but I'm not as fluent in Mandarin as Zuckerberg is."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13738.0,
      "end_time": 16253.0,
      "text": "Thank you everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16253.0,
      "end_time": 18870.0,
      "text": "I'd like to talk with you a little bit about"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18870.0,
      "end_time": 20849.0,
      "text": "what we call \"The 100-Year Plan\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20849.0,
      "end_time": 23787.0,
      "text": "If you think about a time-honored tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23787.0,
      "end_time": 26032.0,
      "text": "usually when you have individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26032.0,
      "end_time": 27320.0,
      "text": "that you care about, that you love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27320.0,
      "end_time": 31747.0,
      "text": "you usually move on with something to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31747.0,
      "end_time": 32964.0,
      "text": "Whether it be a watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32964.0,
      "end_time": 34854.0,
      "text": "whether it be a piece of furniture or what not."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34854.0,
      "end_time": 36117.0,
      "text": "That's what I really want to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36117.0,
      "end_time": 38881.0,
      "text": "with everyone this afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 38881.0,
      "end_time": 39857.0,
      "text": "Let's go back in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 39857.0,
      "end_time": 43697.0,
      "text": "Let's go back to sometime in the early '70s."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 43697.0,
      "end_time": 48420.0,
      "text": "Consumer electronics companies actually had a vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48420.0,
      "end_time": 51891.0,
      "text": "of longevity of product design."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51891.0,
      "end_time": 54560.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it hasn't played out necessarily"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54560.0,
      "end_time": 57650.0,
      "text": "the way they had envisioned in their advertising."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57650.0,
      "end_time": 59331.0,
      "text": "This could be the tape deck"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59331.0,
      "end_time": 60964.0,
      "text": "you would leave with your grandson."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60964.0,
      "end_time": 61838.0,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 61838.0,
      "end_time": 64427.0,
      "text": "I don't think this is really a Rolex."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 64427.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67418.0,
      "text": "A Rolex does stand the test of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67418.0,
      "end_time": 69724.0,
      "text": "But, we believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 69724.0,
      "end_time": 71165.0,
      "text": "my co-founders and I,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 71165.0,
      "end_time": 73256.0,
      "text": "Aubrey Anderson, Jason Proctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 73256.0,
      "end_time": 74785.0,
      "text": "those of us in Monohm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74785.0,
      "end_time": 77267.0,
      "text": "that there is a chance for a 100 year plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 77267.0,
      "end_time": 80023.0,
      "text": "and there's also an opportunity to share this vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 80023.0,
      "end_time": 81924.0,
      "text": "to other new start-ups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 81924.0,
      "end_time": 83659.0,
      "text": "other consumer electronics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83659.0,
      "end_time": 87253.0,
      "text": "other product design companies around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87253.0,
      "end_time": 90790.0,
      "text": "Especially as it relates to this new medium"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90790.0,
      "end_time": 94453.0,
      "text": "of Internet of Things and wearables."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 94453.0,
      "end_time": 97284.0,
      "text": "Over the course of my two decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97284.0,
      "end_time": 99530.0,
      "text": "of working in this industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 99530.0,
      "end_time": 102534.0,
      "text": "I'd have to say that a lot of the experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 102534.0,
      "end_time": 104005.0,
      "text": "and products that I've worked on"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 104005.0,
      "end_time": 106007.0,
      "text": "have unfortunately ended up"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106007.0,
      "end_time": 108226.0,
      "text": "at the top of the e-waste pile."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108226.0,
      "end_time": 110552.0,
      "text": "Usually the life span of one of our particular products"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 110552.0,
      "end_time": 111537.0,
      "text": "that we would make"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 111537.0,
      "end_time": 113263.0,
      "text": "usually lasts only about two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 113263.0,
      "end_time": 116259.0,
      "text": "So when we formed this new company, Monohm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116259.0,
      "end_time": 117776.0,
      "text": "we thought really hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 117776.0,
      "end_time": 119714.0,
      "text": "We did a lot of internal soul-searching."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 119714.0,
      "end_time": 121777.0,
      "text": "And this is interesting, because coming from America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 121777.0,
      "end_time": 124320.0,
      "text": "we don't really think past maybe 30, 40, or 50 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 124320.0,
      "end_time": 126480.0,
      "text": "We're trying to think 100 years out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 126480.0,
      "end_time": 128448.0,
      "text": "something that is generational."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 128448.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133477.0,
      "text": "We said, \"If we were going to make an object"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 133477.0,
      "end_time": 135097.0,
      "text": "that would be part of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 135097.0,
      "end_time": 138048.0,
      "text": "how can we make it sustain 100 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 138048.0,
      "end_time": 139365.0,
      "text": "or even longer?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139365.0,
      "end_time": 142011.0,
      "text": "So we sought out experts, individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 142011.0,
      "end_time": 147096.0,
      "text": "that are also like-minded within this thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 147096.0,
      "end_time": 148728.0,
      "text": "We break this down into three phases."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148728.0,
      "end_time": 151620.0,
      "text": "I'm going to take you through each of the three phases."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151620.0,
      "end_time": 155001.0,
      "text": "The first is sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 155001.0,
      "end_time": 158109.0,
      "text": "As one of the earlier speakers this afternoon said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158109.0,
      "end_time": 160611.0,
      "text": "\"It's not a matter of doing green architecture or green design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160611.0,
      "end_time": 162073.0,
      "text": "every design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162073.0,
      "end_time": 165147.0,
      "text": "every environmental experience should be green.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165147.0,
      "end_time": 166836.0,
      "text": "And I believe that as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 166836.0,
      "end_time": 169814.0,
      "text": "I also think that when you create the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169814.0,
      "end_time": 172021.0,
      "text": "of the product that you're going to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 172021.0,
      "end_time": 174875.0,
      "text": "essentially sharing with your world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174875.0,
      "end_time": 176109.0,
      "text": "those that you care about"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176109.0,
      "end_time": 179677.0,
      "text": "those that will inherit this particular experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179677.0,
      "end_time": 182650.0,
      "text": "you need to think about what's going to go into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 182650.0,
      "end_time": 185076.0,
      "text": "One of the things that we've been looking into is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185076.0,
      "end_time": 187916.0,
      "text": "we do have a trash problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 187916.0,
      "end_time": 189079.0,
      "text": "How can you make something"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 189079.0,
      "end_time": 191419.0,
      "text": "that can stand the test of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 191419.0,
      "end_time": 194866.0,
      "text": "and also try to fix that unique issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 194866.0,
      "end_time": 198372.0,
      "text": "and not contribute back to the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 198372.0,
      "end_time": 200959.0,
      "text": "There's a huge cesspool of PET bottles and trash"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 200959.0,
      "end_time": 204609.0,
      "text": "coming from our region, the Pacific Ocean region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 204609.0,
      "end_time": 206110.0,
      "text": "in the North Pacific."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 206110.0,
      "end_time": 207698.0,
      "text": "We were looking at and studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 207698.0,
      "end_time": 209460.0,
      "text": "how can we build something"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 209460.0,
      "end_time": 211257.0,
      "text": "that's beautiful and architectural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 211257.0,
      "end_time": 212739.0,
      "text": "something that is really akin"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212739.0,
      "end_time": 214673.0,
      "text": "that would last 100 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 214673.0,
      "end_time": 216434.0,
      "text": "We're looking to new material sciences"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 216434.0,
      "end_time": 218602.0,
      "text": "and how companies like Envision Plastics"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 218602.0,
      "end_time": 222573.0,
      "text": "can reclaim these objects that were once created"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 222573.0,
      "end_time": 226530.0,
      "text": "and then disregarded into our ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 226530.0,
      "end_time": 228698.0,
      "text": "What can we actually make with that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 228698.0,
      "end_time": 230832.0,
      "text": "So we got together with a few of our"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 230832.0,
      "end_time": 233629.0,
      "text": "also close-minded, like-minded friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 233629.0,
      "end_time": 235285.0,
      "text": "one of which is SurfaceInk."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 235285.0,
      "end_time": 237939.0,
      "text": "They are also applying this philosophy"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 237939.0,
      "end_time": 241652.0,
      "text": "into the future products that they're making today."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 241652.0,
      "end_time": 243406.0,
      "text": "This is one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243406.0,
      "end_time": 247831.0,
      "text": "It's a toy that's intended to really stand the test of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 247831.0,
      "end_time": 250097.0,
      "text": "in the wear and tear of young individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 250097.0,
      "end_time": 251330.0,
      "text": "But it's also sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 251330.0,
      "end_time": 255753.0,
      "text": "It's created from collecting the waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 255753.0,
      "end_time": 259694.0,
      "text": "putting it into an experience that the children will enjoy."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 259694.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261751.00000000003,
      "text": "Yet it can gracefully degrade"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 261750.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263675.0,
      "text": "and go back into the ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 263675.0,
      "end_time": 265882.0,
      "text": "The toy was designed so that it can be taken apart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 265882.0,
      "end_time": 268202.0,
      "text": "and also be disassembled and put back"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 268202.0,
      "end_time": 270655.0,
      "text": "and recycled into something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 270655.0,
      "end_time": 273590.0,
      "text": "This is the like-minded thinking that we are inspired by"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273590.0,
      "end_time": 277783.0,
      "text": "and that we are building our new company around."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 277783.0,
      "end_time": 281938.0,
      "text": "Heirloom is another key pinnacle of"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281938.0,
      "end_time": 285599.0,
      "text": "what we see as part of the 100 year plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 285599.0,
      "end_time": 288189.0,
      "text": "If you think about heirloom as I mentioned earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 288189.0,
      "end_time": 290723.0,
      "text": "as an example with the Sony tape deck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 290723.0,
      "end_time": 292481.0,
      "text": "(my dad actually had one of those..."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 292481.0,
      "end_time": 294021.0,
      "text": "I probably still have it in the garage..."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 294021.0,
      "end_time": 299377.0,
      "text": "maybe with Saturday Night Fever soundtrack),"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 299377.0,
      "end_time": 303282.0,
      "text": "you want to be able to give something."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 303282.0,
      "end_time": 307267.0,
      "text": "Even if it's a piece of electronics"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 307267.0,
      "end_time": 309424.0,
      "text": "that you might be able to still display it"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 309424.0,
      "end_time": 311051.0,
      "text": "on your mantle, put it on your desk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 311051.0,
      "end_time": 312814.0,
      "text": "and it still becomes a part of your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 312814.0,
      "end_time": 315460.0,
      "text": "that you're passing down to a generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 315460.0,
      "end_time": 316847.0,
      "text": "When you think about heirlooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 316847.0,
      "end_time": 318844.0,
      "text": "it's not necessarily something that would"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 318844.0,
      "end_time": 320584.0,
      "text": "come out of the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 320584.0,
      "end_time": 323374.0,
      "text": "But there are also another set of like-minded individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 323374.0,
      "end_time": 325306.0,
      "text": "that we're working very closely with"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 325306.0,
      "end_time": 327231.0,
      "text": "around this particular challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 327231.0,
      "end_time": 329032.0,
      "text": "Box Clever being one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 329032.0,
      "end_time": 331104.0,
      "text": "A good example of something that can be passed down"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 331104.0,
      "end_time": 332766.0,
      "text": "is essentially furniture."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 332766.0,
      "end_time": 335042.0,
      "text": "If you think about the one object"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 335042.0,
      "end_time": 336960.0,
      "text": "that stands the test of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 336960.0,
      "end_time": 338444.0,
      "text": "it's something that we use everyday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 338444.0,
      "end_time": 339403.0,
      "text": "it's functional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 339403.0,
      "end_time": 342552.0,
      "text": "it can be inherited down generationally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 342552.0,
      "end_time": 343900.0,
      "text": "that is definitely furniture."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 343900.0,
      "end_time": 346624.0,
      "text": "They set out for the most recent Poise project"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 346624.0,
      "end_time": 349092.0,
      "text": "to create a set of extensible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 349092.0,
      "end_time": 352309.0,
      "text": "very enriching objects that generationally"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 352309.0,
      "end_time": 355720.0,
      "text": "will hold up and patina over the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 355720.0,
      "end_time": 358990.0,
      "text": "that will just gracefully integrate within one's lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 358990.0,
      "end_time": 360656.0,
      "text": "The best object that anyone can design"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 360656.0,
      "end_time": 362356.0,
      "text": "is something that's really invisible"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 362356.0,
      "end_time": 364042.0,
      "text": "and that you really depend on"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 364042.0,
      "end_time": 368038.0,
      "text": "and it just integrates within your own life."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 368038.0,
      "end_time": 370127.0,
      "text": "I think that they really have accomplished this."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 370127.0,
      "end_time": 371962.0,
      "text": "And this is a really good example"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 371962.0,
      "end_time": 373273.0,
      "text": "that inspires us to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 373273.0,
      "end_time": 377666.0,
      "text": "and deliver that heirloom quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 377666.0,
      "end_time": 380322.0,
      "text": "Another example, and this is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 380322.0,
      "end_time": 382646.0,
      "text": "that probably will resonate with"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 382646.0,
      "end_time": 385383.0,
      "text": "all of you here in Taipei."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 385383.0,
      "end_time": 388480.0,
      "text": "A good friend of mine, Alexander Bazes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 388480.0,
      "end_time": 389409.0,
      "text": "changed careers."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 389409.0,
      "end_time": 390865.0,
      "text": "We were just talking about entrepreneurship and"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 390865.0,
      "end_time": 393441.0,
      "text": "re-inventing yourself a little bit earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 393441.0,
      "end_time": 395321.0,
      "text": "What Alex did, was..."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 395321.0,
      "end_time": 398302.0,
      "text": "he was a PhD philosophy student"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 398302.0,
      "end_time": 400020.0,
      "text": "at the University of Kyoto"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 400020.0,
      "end_time": 401609.0,
      "text": "who essentially decided,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 401609.0,
      "end_time": 403108.0,
      "text": "\"I'm going to make swords."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 403108.0,
      "end_time": 405711.0,
      "text": "I'm going to make knives in the traditional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 405711.0,
      "end_time": 408291.0,
      "text": "samurai blacksmithing technique.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 408291.0,
      "end_time": 410867.0,
      "text": "And he went back, and he found a mountain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 410867.0,
      "end_time": 413246.0,
      "text": "and he started working on his craft."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 413246.0,
      "end_time": 415581.0,
      "text": "And he's applying that heritage mentality"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 415581.0,
      "end_time": 418025.0,
      "text": "of creating some really exquisite..."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 418025.0,
      "end_time": 423029.0,
      "text": "(This is a picture of him in his outdoor setting)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 423029.0,
      "end_time": 425284.0,
      "text": "knives that really..."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 425284.0,
      "end_time": 427512.0,
      "text": "If you think about using the material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 427512.0,
      "end_time": 430311.0,
      "text": "building something that can stand and wear"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 430311.0,
      "end_time": 432297.0,
      "text": "with the test of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 432297.0,
      "end_time": 434888.0,
      "text": "that is something that I believe we should all"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 434888.0,
      "end_time": 438266.0,
      "text": "fall back to with our product design"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 438266.0,
      "end_time": 440538.0,
      "text": "in the near future."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 440538.0,
      "end_time": 443022.0,
      "text": "Something to note about these types of technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 443022.0,
      "end_time": 444868.0,
      "text": "whether it's metal, whether it's ceramics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 444868.0,
      "end_time": 447620.0,
      "text": "whether it's reclaimed sustainable materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 447620.0,
      "end_time": 451281.0,
      "text": "now you'll be able to bring life and intelligence into them."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 451281.0,
      "end_time": 454061.0,
      "text": "You'll be able to add brains, essentially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 454061.0,
      "end_time": 456425.0,
      "text": "creating an nascent object into a smart object."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 456425.0,
      "end_time": 457893.0,
      "text": "And that is what really will surround us"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 457893.0,
      "end_time": 462493.0,
      "text": "within our connected homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 462493.0,
      "end_time": 464095.0,
      "text": "And heritage."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 464095.0,
      "end_time": 466333.0,
      "text": "Heritage is something that within the 100 year plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 466333.0,
      "end_time": 468915.0,
      "text": "I think in order for you to sustain that longevity"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 468915.0,
      "end_time": 471459.0,
      "text": "of the product experiences that you're trying to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 471459.0,
      "end_time": 473771.0,
      "text": "that can be passed down generationally"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 473771.0,
      "end_time": 475322.0,
      "text": "as an heirloom object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 475322.0,
      "end_time": 477210.0,
      "text": "you wanna instill a sense of heritage."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 477210.0,
      "end_time": 479126.0,
      "text": "And that's something a lot of us can learn from"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 479126.0,
      "end_time": 481284.0,
      "text": "a lot of the Swiss companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 481284.0,
      "end_time": 484149.0,
      "text": "the European couture brands."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 484149.0,
      "end_time": 487394.0,
      "text": "We're working very closely with a group of artisans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 487394.0,
      "end_time": 489452.0,
      "text": "handcraft artisans in Kyoto,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 489452.0,
      "end_time": 492078.0,
      "text": "studying, discussing, engaging with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 492078.0,
      "end_time": 495100.0,
      "text": "around their craft and how their craft can be utilized"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 495100.0,
      "end_time": 497724.0,
      "text": "in some of our thinking and some of the future ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 497724.0,
      "end_time": 500666.0,
      "text": "that we're going to be bringing to market."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 500666.0,
      "end_time": 503480.0,
      "text": "We call this collaboration \"Kyoto California\","
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 503480.0,
      "end_time": 505080.0,
      "text": "or \"Kyo-Cali\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 505080.0,
      "end_time": 506744.0,
      "text": "Essentially, the thinking behind this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 506744.0,
      "end_time": 508603.0,
      "text": "and this could be Taipei and California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 508603.0,
      "end_time": 511588.0,
      "text": "this could be London and Beijing."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 511588.0,
      "end_time": 513668.0,
      "text": "The thinking about this is to take"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 513668.0,
      "end_time": 517113.0,
      "text": "something that's of heritage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 517113.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520015.00000000006,
      "text": "a craftsman experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 520015.0,
      "end_time": 521432.0,
      "text": "and melding it with the modern."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 521432.0,
      "end_time": 522992.0,
      "text": "Melding it with the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 522991.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525593.0,
      "text": "and the infrastructure and the entrepreneurship"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 525593.0,
      "end_time": 526944.0,
      "text": "of a particular area."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 526944.0,
      "end_time": 529278.0,
      "text": "And in this case, it's Silicon Valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 529278.0,
      "end_time": 532366.0,
      "text": "Because of the fusion of the two disciplines"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 532366.0,
      "end_time": 535400.0,
      "text": "and experiences in knowledge colliding together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 535400.0,
      "end_time": 537092.0,
      "text": "it will generate new ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 537092.0,
      "end_time": 540532.0,
      "text": "that never would have been envisioned."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 540532.0,
      "end_time": 544351.0,
      "text": "And that's part of the 100-year plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 544351.0,
      "end_time": 546816.0,
      "text": "Kaikado. Takahiro Yagi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 546816.0,
      "end_time": 548641.0,
      "text": "who is an amazing craftsman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 548641.0,
      "end_time": 551293.0,
      "text": "and inside of his family business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 551293.0,
      "end_time": 553944.0,
      "text": "who, generationally, dating all the way back"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 553944.0,
      "end_time": 556893.0,
      "text": "to the early days when Kyoto was the capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 556893.0,
      "end_time": 559804.0,
      "text": "has been making some amazing canisters"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 559804.0,
      "end_time": 565210.0,
      "text": "that have also started in a really refined, executed"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 565210.0,
      "end_time": 568281.0,
      "text": "use of storing tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 568281.0,
      "end_time": 570849.0,
      "text": "But through the use of bringing back heirloom metals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 570849.0,
      "end_time": 572768.0,
      "text": "how the metals were made hundreds of years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 572768.0,
      "end_time": 574257.0,
      "text": "bringing that mentality back"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 574257.0,
      "end_time": 577902.0,
      "text": "into delivering these next-generation products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 577902.0,
      "end_time": 580853.0,
      "text": "he's expanded so that now they meet the needs of"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 580853.0,
      "end_time": 585013.0,
      "text": "chefs around the world for pasta or for coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 585013.0,
      "end_time": 587593.0,
      "text": "One of the incredible things about"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 587593.0,
      "end_time": 589294.0,
      "text": "the particular products that he makes..."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 589294.0,
      "end_time": 594099.0,
      "text": "(and I brought one with me just to show everyone)"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 594099.0,
      "end_time": 598583.0,
      "text": "This is a brand-new tea canister."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 598583.0,
      "end_time": 602304.0,
      "text": "Yet it has the finish of a 100-year object."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 602304.0,
      "end_time": 605186.0,
      "text": "That's also the thought and thinking that went into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 605186.0,
      "end_time": 607223.0,
      "text": "Of the patina, how do you advance the patina?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 607223.0,
      "end_time": 610135.0,
      "text": "So it might be initially really shiny like these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 610135.0,
      "end_time": 613375.0,
      "text": "but you can advance the aging and wearing of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 613375.0,
      "end_time": 615372.0,
      "text": "The other thing that's really impressive"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 615372.0,
      "end_time": 617884.0,
      "text": "about this thinking of the 100-year plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 617884.0,
      "end_time": 619967.0,
      "text": "is that this has incredible warrantee."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 619967.0,
      "end_time": 621700.0,
      "text": "You can bring it back 60 years from now"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 621700.0,
      "end_time": 623772.0,
      "text": "and they'll fix it."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 623772.0,
      "end_time": 625519.0,
      "text": "And that really comes down to the precision"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 625519.0,
      "end_time": 628401.0,
      "text": "of hundreds of a millimeter that they have"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 628401.0,
      "end_time": 630840.0,
      "text": "of hand making."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 630840.0,
      "end_time": 632390.0,
      "text": "The closure mechanism."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 632390.0,
      "end_time": 634535.0,
      "text": "It's closing itself just by dropping it"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 634535.0,
      "end_time": 637867.0,
      "text": "upon the top and flushing all the air out."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 637867.0,
      "end_time": 640662.0,
      "text": "That is incredible craftsmanship."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 640662.0,
      "end_time": 643137.0,
      "text": "And that is something that I'd like to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 643137.0,
      "end_time": 645475.0,
      "text": "everyone of you that is in this audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 645475.0,
      "end_time": 648001.0,
      "text": "as a designer, as an entrepreneur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 648001.0,
      "end_time": 649750.0,
      "text": "as a large corporation to apply"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 649750.0,
      "end_time": 655434.0,
      "text": "towards all the product thinking that you do going forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 655434.0,
      "end_time": 656987.0,
      "text": "Textiles is also something"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 656987.0,
      "end_time": 659695.0,
      "text": "that's really interesting to us right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 659695.0,
      "end_time": 664222.0,
      "text": "How do you apply textiles within electronics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 664222.0,
      "end_time": 665904.0,
      "text": "This is Hosoo."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 665904.0,
      "end_time": 668790.0,
      "text": "They're also a many generational"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 668790.0,
      "end_time": 671803.0,
      "text": "craftsman family in Kyoto,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 671803.0,
      "end_time": 674532.0,
      "text": "who predominately has been known for"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 674532.0,
      "end_time": 677425.0,
      "text": "kimono-making, but they've got into"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 677425.0,
      "end_time": 678849.0,
      "text": "product design."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 678849.0,
      "end_time": 681881.0,
      "text": "The types of fabrics they're working on right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 681881.0,
      "end_time": 683848.0,
      "text": "are just absolutely amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 683848.0,
      "end_time": 685758.0,
      "text": "They have 3D properties to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 685758.0,
      "end_time": 689785.0,
      "text": "It's not just the sensualness of looking at the fabric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 689785.0,
      "end_time": 694781.0,
      "text": "but it's touching it, and the ripples and the textures."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 694781.0,
      "end_time": 697638.0,
      "text": "Here's an example of a piece of fabric that they've done"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 697638.0,
      "end_time": 699608.0,
      "text": "that also has a 3D texture mapped onto"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 699608.0,
      "end_time": 703216.0,
      "text": "two different treatments: black and red."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 703216.0,
      "end_time": 706401.0,
      "text": "Use your imagination using these heritage materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 706401.0,
      "end_time": 707877.0,
      "text": "and try to think about how you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 707877.0,
      "end_time": 710365.0,
      "text": "create new experiences and objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 710365.0,
      "end_time": 713044.0,
      "text": "that can be sustainably handed down"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 713044.0,
      "end_time": 716081.0,
      "text": "over the decades to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 716081.0,
      "end_time": 719488.0,
      "text": "They're collaborating on some old-school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 719488.0,
      "end_time": 721088.0,
      "text": "old-world techniques of how you"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 721088.0,
      "end_time": 723722.0,
      "text": "like you saw the machine that makes the fabric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 723722.0,
      "end_time": 727089.0,
      "text": "but they're also looking at future materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 727089.0,
      "end_time": 728777.0,
      "text": "such as polymer resins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 728777.0,
      "end_time": 731314.0,
      "text": "and how do you fuse resin with fabric"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 731314.0,
      "end_time": 734667.0,
      "text": "for this French designer handbag line."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 734667.0,
      "end_time": 736132.0,
      "text": "That's really innovative thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 736132.0,
      "end_time": 738236.0,
      "text": "that I really haven't seen very much of"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 738236.0,
      "end_time": 742102.0,
      "text": "in the past 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 742102.0,
      "end_time": 747227.0,
      "text": "And then lastly, thinking about taking from the earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 747227.0,
      "end_time": 749033.0,
      "text": "using it, and then eventually in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 749033.0,
      "end_time": 751066.0,
      "text": "returning it to the earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 751066.0,
      "end_time": 756351.0,
      "text": "Another company, Kohchosai Kosuga,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 756351.0,
      "end_time": 758668.0,
      "text": "has been working with lacquer bamboo"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 758668.0,
      "end_time": 763640.0,
      "text": "to deliver really exceptional experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 763640.0,
      "end_time": 766243.0,
      "text": "that really are used in different disciplines."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 766243.0,
      "end_time": 768198.0,
      "text": "So here we have an example of a lamp"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 768198.0,
      "end_time": 770855.0,
      "text": "that they've done, but they do"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 770855.0,
      "end_time": 773737.0,
      "text": "starting off with just very hairline strips of bamboo"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 773737.0,
      "end_time": 776857.0,
      "text": "that could be really soft and supple to touch"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 776857.0,
      "end_time": 778870.0,
      "text": "and then weave them into things that are"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 778870.0,
      "end_time": 781898.0,
      "text": "baskets for ikebana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 781898.0,
      "end_time": 783778.0,
      "text": "or purses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 783778.0,
      "end_time": 786955.0,
      "text": "or really soft pieces of wallets"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 786955.0,
      "end_time": 790659.0,
      "text": "that feel like leather but it's all made out of bamboo."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 790659.0,
      "end_time": 793525.0,
      "text": "This type of thinking, this synergetic collision"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 793525.0,
      "end_time": 795932.0,
      "text": "of product design, old-world heritage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 795932.0,
      "end_time": 798461.0,
      "text": "and technology, \"Kyo-Cali\","
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 798461.0,
      "end_time": 800108.0,
      "text": "we would like to start exploring"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 800108.0,
      "end_time": 802574.0,
      "text": "with other parts of the world as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 802574.0,
      "end_time": 804109.0,
      "text": "And so I encourage all of you later on"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 804109.0,
      "end_time": 806821.0,
      "text": "to come up and have a discussion with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 806821.0,
      "end_time": 808054.0,
      "text": "We'd love to share a little bit more"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 808054.0,
      "end_time": 809545.0,
      "text": "about what our thinking is"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 809545.0,
      "end_time": 813484.0,
      "text": "and what we're up to."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 813484.0,
      "end_time": 815295.0,
      "text": "It all ties into what we consider to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 815295.0,
      "end_time": 817341.0,
      "text": "the \"new necessities\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 817341.0,
      "end_time": 819373.0,
      "text": "Things that we want to bring into our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 819373.0,
      "end_time": 820770.0,
      "text": "that really excite us."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 820770.0,
      "end_time": 824475.0,
      "text": "These architectural objects that basically"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 824475.0,
      "end_time": 830138.0,
      "text": "transcend into the 100-year experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 830138.0,
      "end_time": 832253.0,
      "text": "We call these \"heirloom for the future\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 832253.0,
      "end_time": 833229.0,
      "text": "And we'll be talking more about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 833229.0,
      "end_time": 837193.0,
      "text": "in the months to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 837193.0,
      "end_time": 838733.0,
      "text": "Please remember to think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 838733.0,
      "end_time": 839885.0,
      "text": "the materials you're choosing."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 839885.0,
      "end_time": 841635.0,
      "text": "Make sure that they're sustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 841635.0,
      "end_time": 844858.0,
      "text": "they're holistic, that you're thinking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 844858.0,
      "end_time": 847468.0,
      "text": "the heirloom aspect of what you're making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 847468.0,
      "end_time": 848933.0,
      "text": "that it's not going to end"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 848933.0,
      "end_time": 852487.0,
      "text": "at the top of the e-waste pile."
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 852487.0,
      "end_time": 854510.0,
      "text": "And then also think about the longevity"
    },
    {
      "index": 334,
      "start_time": 854510.0,
      "end_time": 857074.0,
      "text": "from a heritage perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 335,
      "start_time": 857074.0,
      "end_time": 858671.0,
      "text": "Building your own brand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 336,
      "start_time": 858671.0,
      "end_time": 861260.0,
      "text": "collaborating with existing, established brands."
    },
    {
      "index": 337,
      "start_time": 861260.0,
      "end_time": 864008.0,
      "text": "To really bring to our world something that's exceptional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 338,
      "start_time": 864008.0,
      "end_time": 866951.0,
      "text": "and can be appreciated immensely."
    },
    {
      "index": 339,
      "start_time": 866951.0,
      "end_time": 868799.0,
      "text": "Think about the younger generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 340,
      "start_time": 868799.0,
      "end_time": 870642.0,
      "text": "I always think about my son."
    },
    {
      "index": 341,
      "start_time": 870642.0,
      "end_time": 872023.0,
      "text": "This is him standing on the beach"
    },
    {
      "index": 342,
      "start_time": 872023.0,
      "end_time": 875684.0,
      "text": "at Kirby Cove in San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 343,
      "start_time": 875684.0,
      "end_time": 889000.0,
      "text": "So with that, thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 344,
      "start_time": 889000.0,
      "end_time": 899000.0,
      "text": "Subtitles by the Amara.org community"
    }
  ]
}